  %% Data flow
  IDRes -->|Secure API Calls| APIGW
  APIGW --> ALB --> ECS
  ECS -->|Bulk API| OS
  ECS -->|Reads| S3_delta

  %% ETL Flow
  S3_raw --> Glue
  Glue -->|Delta Calc + File Gen| S3_delta
  Glue --> GlueCatalog
  Glue -->|Archive| S3_archive
  SF --> Glue

  %% Security Connections
  IAM --> Glue
  IAM --> ECS
  KMS --> S3_raw
  KMS --> OS
  CW --> ECS
  CW --> Glue
  Guard --> IAM

  %% On-Prem connectivity
  VPN --> APIGW
  VPN --> ECS
